rows.label: qst201304_msg0001
rows.name: You want to know where Shamal-kun went?

rows.label: qst201304_msg0002
rows.name:
He hasn't come here to play
recently. We weren't that
close to begin with...

rows.label: qst201304_msg0003
rows.name:
I just thought he found
a better place to play.

rows.label: qst201304_msg0004
rows.name: I hope you find him soon.
